## 3. State Management

| State Type | Solution | Scope | Example |
|------------|----------|-------|---------|
| **Server State** | TanStack Query (React Query) | Global | Dashboard data, team lists, appraisal drafts, calibration metrics |
| **Client State** | Zustand | Global | Auth user, UI theme, sidebar open/close, notification toast queue |
| **Form State** | React Hook Form + Zod | Local | Context submission, override editor, artifact upload |
| **URL State** | React Router v6 | Global | Query params (filters, selected employee), route params (appraisal ID) |

**State Management Rules:**
- All API data в†’ React Query (caching, background refetch, optimistic updates)
- User session & permissions в†’ Zustand (persisted to localStorage)
- Form inputs в†’ React Hook Form (local component state)
- URL filters в†’ React Router `useSearchParams`

